1 AN ACT concerning
2 Public Schools – Water Safety and Swimming – Instructional Content, Plan, and
3 Reporting
4 FOR the purpose of requiring each county board of education to develop certain
5 instructional content on water safety and swimming for public school students in the
6 county; requiring each county board to develop a certain plan regarding access to
7 swimming pools and related facilities for a certain purpose; requiring that the
8 instructional content be offered to students in certain grade bands; and generally
9 relating to water safety and swimming and county boards of education instruction.
10 BY adding to
11 Article – Education
12 Section 7–452
